movie.title: Togo
movie.plot: The story of Togo, the sled dog who led the 1925 serum run yet was considered by most to be too small and weak to lead such an intense race.

events.title: Leonhard Seppala and Togo pick up a diphtheria serum in Shaktoolik
Leonhard Seppala and Togo pass the diphtheria serum they are carrying to another team in Golovin
